{
  "id": "69e6f1f40fe111ddd82b1172",
  "title": "井戸端田螺奇譚",
  "created": 1776742902,
  "updated": 1776747828,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e6f1f40fe111ddd82b1172",
      "text": "井戸端田螺奇譚",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742902,
      "updated": 1776742902
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f1f6000000000061499a",
      "text": "#井戸端でしょうもないページを作る部",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742902,
      "updated": 1776745029
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f24100000000006149a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742977,
      "updated": 1776742977
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f1f9000000000061499e",
      "text": "地域",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742906,
      "updated": 1776744270
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f1fb000000000061499f",
      "text": "\tKT府小扇子市（こせんす）井戸端村（いどばたむら）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743893,
      "updated": 1776745814
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f74f00000000006149d7",
      "text": "\t\t昔はこの辺り一帯のことを野田（のた）と読んでいた",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744271,
      "updated": 1776745788
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fd5c0000000000614a02",
      "text": "\t\t平成の大合併により野田周辺の市町村が合併され、小扇子市となった",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745820,
      "updated": 1776745859
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f23700000000006149a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742967,
      "updated": 1776742985
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2ac00000000006149ac",
      "text": "名所",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743085,
      "updated": 1776744916
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2cb00000000006149ae",
      "text": "\t井戸端の大井戸",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743115,
      "updated": 1776743120
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2d500000000006149af",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端村の貴重な水源地",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743125,
      "updated": 1776743134
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2de00000000006149b0",
      "text": "\t\tなぜかKT府なのにカルデラ湖みたいなのがある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743134,
      "updated": 1776745867
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f61f00000000006149ce",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれを指して「井戸端の大井戸」と呼称されている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743967,
      "updated": 1776743979
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2f700000000006149b1",
      "text": "\t\tここの水源は透き通っており、大変美味しい水源地として知られる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743159,
      "updated": 1776744929
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f63000000000006149cf",
      "text": "\t\tこの水域には[イドバタニシ]が多数棲息しており、井戸端村では甘辛く炊き上げた甘露煮として昔から食されて来た",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743985,
      "updated": 1776744038
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2ad00000000006149ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743085,
      "updated": 1776743085
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f52d00000000006149c4",
      "text": "名物",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743726,
      "updated": 1776743729
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f53000000000006149c6",
      "text": "\t[イドバタニシ]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743729,
      "updated": 1776747761
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f53300000000006149c7",
      "text": "\t\t日本でも井戸端の大井戸付近しか棲息しない貴重なタニシ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743731,
      "updated": 1776747765
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f54700000000006149c8",
      "text": "\t\tイドバタニシはそこそこの数が棲息しており、かつ水産資源としてもキチンと管理されている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743751,
      "updated": 1776747736
    },
    {
      "id": "69e704da0000000000614a0c",
      "text": "\t\t\tそのため、今でもイドバタニシは地元の人に食されている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776747739,
      "updated": 1776747791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f57b00000000006149c9",
      "text": "\t\tイドバタニシを[ヒヤヒヤ.icon] にして締めた後、[アツアツ.icon] に甘辛く炊き上げるのが地元の名物料理",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743803,
      "updated": 1776746963
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f6fd00000000006149d6",
      "text": "\t\t\t味はタニシでありながら肉ような感じでもあり、独特の歯応えがあるそう /red",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744189,
      "updated": 1776744335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f52e00000000006149c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743726,
      "updated": 1776743726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f31000000000006149b2",
      "text": "過去の起きた事件",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743185,
      "updated": 1776743190
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f31500000000006149b4",
      "text": "\t井戸端村の高校生失踪事件",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743190,
      "updated": 1776747816
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f31f00000000006149b5",
      "text": "\t\tその昔、とある高校生が井戸端の大井戸へ遊びにいった後、失踪したいう事件があった",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743199,
      "updated": 1776743961
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f42300000000006149bd",
      "text": "\t\t\t井戸端の大井戸へ続く道へはその子の靴が脱ぎ捨てられていた",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743460,
      "updated": 1776747828
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f43a00000000006149be",
      "text": "\t\t当時、井戸端村では大規模な捜索体制が敷かれたが、大きな進展はなく、その高校生は見付からなかった",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743482,
      "updated": 1776743521
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f33400000000006149b6",
      "text": "\t\tその後、井戸端の大井戸へ続く道へは鍵が掛けられるようになった",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743220,
      "updated": 1776744956
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f36000000000006149b7",
      "text": "\t\t\tその鍵の管理をやっているのが竜華家である",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743265,
      "updated": 1776743277
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f4c400000000006149c0",
      "text": "\t井戸端村の村民失踪事件",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743620,
      "updated": 1776743629
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f4cc00000000006149c1",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端村で時折起きる失踪事件",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743629,
      "updated": 1776743664
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f4f000000000006149c2",
      "text": "\t\t大半は井戸端村を突如離れた、というだけの話だが、時々奇妙な点も含まれている /red",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743664,
      "updated": 1776747196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f31100000000006149b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743185,
      "updated": 1776743185
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f24900000000006149a5",
      "text": "人物・家系",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742985,
      "updated": 1776743371
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f24c00000000006149a6",
      "text": "\t増井先生",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742988,
      "updated": 1776742996
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f25300000000006149a7",
      "text": "\t\t今の小扇子市の礎を気づいた大学の先生",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742996,
      "updated": 1776745907
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f37900000000006149b8",
      "text": "\t\t\t小さな地方都市であった小扇子市の発展に尽力した存命の人物",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743289,
      "updated": 1776743711
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f26600000000006149a8",
      "text": "\t\t今は小扇子市発の大企業 Helpfeel の社屋の前にはこの先生の銅像がある（といううわさ）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743014,
      "updated": 1776743362
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f28800000000006149aa",
      "text": "\t竜華家",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743048,
      "updated": 1776743367
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f2a800000000006149ab",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端の大井戸の[鍵を預けられた人]の家系・地元の名家",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743080,
      "updated": 1776743564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f47e00000000006149bf",
      "text": "\t\t単に鍵を預けられているだけであって、大井戸の歴史に詳しい訳ではない",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743550,
      "updated": 1776743593
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f3e200000000006149bc",
      "text": "\t\t次代の当主は今大学院生らしい、と人々は語っている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776743394,
      "updated": 1776743444
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fa5c00000000006149f2",
      "text": "\t井戸端デシ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745052,
      "updated": 1776745056
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fa6000000000006149f3",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端村発の VTuber",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745056,
      "updated": 1776745063
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fa6700000000006149f4",
      "text": "\t\tその姿は異形であって、可愛らしい少女体の上にリアルな猫の頭が乗っているクリーチャー",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745063,
      "updated": 1776747016
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fa9100000000006149f5",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端村でおきた「しょーもない」話をする雑談配信がメイン",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745105,
      "updated": 1776745135
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6faaf00000000006149f6",
      "text": "\t\t\tその際、 時折怖い話もする /red",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745135,
      "updated": 1776745146
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f1f7000000000061499b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776742903,
      "updated": 1776742903
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f68000000000006149d0",
      "text": "風習",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744064,
      "updated": 1776744067
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f68300000000006149d2",
      "text": "\t[タニシ剥がし]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744067,
      "updated": 1776744075
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f68c00000000006149d3",
      "text": "\t\t文字通りイドバタニシを剥がす行為",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744077,
      "updated": 1776744086
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f69600000000006149d4",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端の大井戸からタニシたちを剥がす漁のこと",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744086,
      "updated": 1776744138
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f6ca00000000006149d5",
      "text": "\t\t近年では水産資源管理の視点から禁漁期間などが定められている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744139,
      "updated": 1776744168
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fe530000000000614a03",
      "text": "\t井戸端の文書（いどばたのもんじょ）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776746068,
      "updated": 1776746209
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fe640000000000614a04",
      "text": "\t\t井戸端村の住人の風習",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776746085,
      "updated": 1776746098
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fe720000000000614a05",
      "text": "\t\t和紙に思い思いの内容を書き、それを村の公民館に集めるという行事",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776746098,
      "updated": 1776746145
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fee80000000000614a08",
      "text": "\t\t\t昔は井戸端神社で行なわれていたが、明治初期に神社が失なわれたため公民館で代用している",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776746217,
      "updated": 1776746277
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fea00000000000614a07",
      "text": "\t\t江戸時代以前から行なわれいた風習であり、それを参考にしたのが Helpfeel 社のグループウェアである",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776746145,
      "updated": 1776746194
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7ec00000000006149de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744429,
      "updated": 1776744429
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7ed00000000006149df",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744429,
      "updated": 1776744449
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f68300000000006149d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744067,
      "updated": 1776744067
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7a900000000006149d8",
      "text": "[KEEP OUT.icon*10]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744362,
      "updated": 1776744382
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7c800000000006149db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744393,
      "updated": 1776744404
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7d400000000006149dc",
      "text": "[* ここから先は井戸端村で起きた奇妙な事案についてのうわさ話である /red]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744404,
      "updated": 1776744981
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7d400000000006149dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744405,
      "updated": 1776744405
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7c600000000006149da",
      "text": "[KEEP OUT.icon*10]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744391,
      "updated": 1776744391
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f7ab00000000006149d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744363,
      "updated": 1776744363
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f80700000000006149e0",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744456,
      "updated": 1776744460
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f80800000000006149e1",
      "text": "[**** 井戸端村での奇妙な出来事]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744456,
      "updated": 1776746298
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f80f00000000006149e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744463,
      "updated": 1776744463
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f83500000000006149e3",
      "text": "突然のイドバタニシ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744501,
      "updated": 1776744577
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f84200000000006149e6",
      "text": "\t井戸端村で人が失踪した際、井戸端の大井戸でまるまると太ったイドバタニシが水揚げされる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744515,
      "updated": 1776744568
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fade00000000006149f7",
      "text": "\tその数は、それまでに失踪していた人間の数と符号するような点があるという",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745182,
      "updated": 1776745220
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6fb0500000000006149f8",
      "text": "\t\t……果たして、それは /red",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776745221,
      "updated": 1776746310
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f83500000000006149e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744501,
      "updated": 1776744501
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f87a00000000006149e7",
      "text": "久檻亜さん",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744570,
      "updated": 1776744758
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f8aa00000000006149e8",
      "text": "\t突如として現われた都市伝説",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744619,
      "updated": 1776744725
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f8d100000000006149e9",
      "text": "\t水色の髪のサイバーな服装をした少女が突然横に立っている、という怪奇現象",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744657,
      "updated": 1776744693
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f8f500000000006149ea",
      "text": " \tその際、その少女は「[ようこそ愚かなホモサピエンス]」と言い、その後すぐに消えるという /red",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744693,
      "updated": 1776746336
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6f91900000000006149ec",
      "text": "\t久檻亜さんについて、特にこれ以外で報告されている事案はない",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776744729,
      "updated": 1776746366
    },
    {
